cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.PL, cs.CC

This paper is about a proof system for quantified Boolean formulas (QBFs), which is a topic in logic and automated reasoning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Additionally, the paper discusses improvements in QBF preprocessing, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The use of propositional unit propagation (UP) and QBF specific UP (QUP) also suggests a connection to data structures (cs.DS) and programming languages (cs.PL).
